    <item>
      <title>特朗普暗示对中国征收关税，黄金价格升至 11 周高点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/gold-xauusd-holds-near-11-week-high-as-trump-hints-at-china-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着总统唐纳德·特朗普继续阐述其对贸易和移民政策的看法，金价攀升至自 11 月初以来的最高盘中水平，交易员们关注着全球经济的前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-22/gold-xauusd-holds-near-11-week-high-as-trump-hints-at-china-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jan 2025 00:54:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普关税威胁引发贸易战担忧，油价延续跌势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-22</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普威胁对中国征收关税，并表示正在考虑对加拿大和墨西哥征收高额关税，此举引发了人们对多条战线爆发贸易战的担忧，油价随之下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-22</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 23:32:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能有望抵消关税风险，股指期货上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 领导下增加人工智能支出的乐观情绪抵消了迫在眉睫的关税带来的不确定性，欧洲和美国的股票期货上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 22:36:17 GMT</pubDate>
